Pickling.

103
00:05:03,220 --> 00:05:04,120
Still dead.

104
00:05:04,150 --> 00:05:05,050
Flambéing!

105
00:05:05,090 --> 00:05:06,350
Nope.

106
00:05:06,390 --> 00:05:07,420
And... CLEAR!

107
00:05:10,730 --> 00:05:12,030
He gone.

108
00:05:12,060 --> 00:05:12,990
Clear harder!

109
00:05:14,660 --> 00:05:17,600
Begging! Please come back,
oh wish-granting sardine.

110
00:05:17,630 --> 00:05:19,470
Johnny, it's me
Flint, we met earlier.

111
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:23,500
JOHNNY!

112
00:05:26,380 --> 00:05:28,010
It's about time! Wah!

113
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:30,580
Why don't we just tell
the Mayor the truth?

114
