Not good ones, but songs!

116
00:05:38,420 --> 00:05:41,690
Hey, come on. They
can't all be hits.

117
00:05:41,730 --> 00:05:43,520
He's not smelling so fresh.

118
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:46,460
I know. I just
wish, I wish...

119
00:05:46,500 --> 00:05:49,460
That's it! I'll just wish Johnny
Sardine back to normal.

120
00:05:49,500 --> 00:05:52,570
I wish for Johnny Sardine
to be good as new.

121
00:05:55,110 --> 00:05:56,600
YOU'RE THE ONE
RESPONSIBLE FOR THIS!

122
