Whoa, Earl, put those pecs
away before you hurt someone.

125
00:06:07,620 --> 00:06:10,420
Again?

126
00:06:15,730 --> 00:06:17,160
I can't believe anyone buys

127
00:06:17,190 --> 00:06:19,190
