I'm a wish-destroyer.
A dream-crusher.

130
00:06:32,180 --> 00:06:34,710
A hope-squashing
fish-squisher.

131
00:06:34,740 --> 00:06:37,650
Relax. They don't
even know it's us.

132
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:39,250
I'M GONNA LOCK YOU UP!

133
