147
00:07:21,690 --> 00:07:26,160
Criminal how tasty your ice
cream is.

148
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:29,460
I only wish my whole body was
a tongue so I could roll up

149
00:07:29,500 --> 00:07:32,470
