It's invasive; it's expensive;
and you will regret it.

152
00:07:38,110 --> 00:07:40,580
We can't stay in
Swallow Falls anymore.

153
00:07:40,610 --> 00:07:43,240
We have to put
as much distance between us

154
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:44,800
