here all day. Whoo!

176
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,530
Whoo!

177
00:08:36,930 --> 00:08:38,570
This town is so weird.

178
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,730
C'mon Sam, JUMP!

179
00:08:39,770 --> 00:08:41,240
Agh!

180
