Drop and give me twenty!

191
00:09:20,780 --> 00:09:22,880
Flint, we have to
tell the truth!

192
00:09:22,910 --> 00:09:25,950
You're right, Sam. Our
days on the lam are over.

193
00:09:25,980 --> 00:09:29,320
No more ruthless renegades
on the run from old man law.

194
00:09:29,350 --> 00:09:31,290
What? We didn't
really run.

195
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,850
We were children
of the universe. What?

196
00:09:32,890 --> 00:09:34,560
...and now we must return.

197
00:09:34,590 --> 00:09:36,890
Thank you, we got it.

198
00:09:36,930 --> 00:09:40,390
Mayor Shelbourne,
fellow Swallow Fallians.

199
00:09:40,430 --> 00:09:42,460
I'm afraid we killed...

200
