Stop the press!
That is not Johnny Sardine.

201
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:49,370
Boo!

202
00:09:49,410 --> 00:09:50,570
Outrageous!

203
00:09:50,610 --> 00:09:51,870
Lies! What's-her-name lies!

204
00:09:51,910 --> 00:09:53,710
The foreign one lies!

205
00:09:53,740 --> 00:09:56,640
No, Sam's right. It's a
Johnny Sardine miracle!

206
00:09:56,680 --> 00:09:59,280
My wish came true!
He's good as new!

207
