for Thursday?

218
00:10:32,920 --> 00:10:37,390
Please. Like I'd do that.

219
00:10:37,420 --> 00:10:39,520
Now it's got an eye
patch and an afro.

220
00:10:39,560 --> 00:10:40,760
Looking good, little fishy.

221
00:10:40,790 --> 00:10:42,390
This town is so weird.

222
00:10:42,430 --> 00:10:43,760
